      Showcase Custom Vinyl Windows and Doors    

Founded in 1994, Showcase Custom Vinyl Windows and Doors manufactures and sells high-quality Earthwise Windows & Doors to leading distributors throughout the Gulf Coast, from Brownsville, Texas, to the Florida panhandle.
We take great pride in our flexibility in serving our customers with any shape and size needed. It is our goal to manufacture our products to our customers’ specifications and delivery schedules, providing the highest degree of customer satisfaction.
From the beginning, Showcase has manufactured only vinyl windows. We focus on manufacturing excellence, unparalleled customer service and enduring quality. Our dedicated customer service team allows us the flexibility to react quickly to our customers’ needs. We are proud of our history of correct, courteous and on-time delivery.
Showcase is a leading manufacturer of vinyl hurricane impact windows and doors for the Gulf Coast, which we offer in a wide range of sizes, configurations and styles. We focus on a low solar heat gain coefficient in our windows to provide premium energy efficiency and savings in the warm climate of the Gulf Coast.
Our Mission
To provide innovative window and door solutions to our customers by manufacturing the very best vinyl windows and doors, delivering them on time, and providing courteous and prompt service during and after delivery.








